    <section id="about" class="about_section_y5t">
        <div class="section_wrapper_t9l">
            <h2 class="section_title_b3k">About GainxHub</h2>
            <div class="about_content_z9x">
                <div class="about_text_l6c">
                    <p>At GainxHub, we believe that great interior design goes beyond aesthetics. Our approach focuses on creating spaces that enhance your daily life, improve functionality, and reflect your personal style.</p>
                    <p>With over 15 years of experience in the industry, our team has successfully completed hundreds of residential and commercial projects. We pride ourselves on our attention to detail, commitment to quality, and ability to work within any budget.</p>
